            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash has had 10 min, add the <strong>chopped pepper</strong>, <strong>halved cherry</strong> <strong>tomatoes</strong> and <strong>ras el hanout </strong>to the baking tray and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>spiced roasted veg</strong></p><p>Return the tray to the oven for a further 10 min or until everything is tender</p>",
